**INSTRUCTIONS:**
  1. Install OpenCV by
      pip install opencv-python
  2. Change the id for every new person 
  3. Locate to your OpenCV location and find **"haarcascade_frontalface_default.xml"** which has set to rules to dectect faces based on proposed properties
  4. Bring it to your code
  5. To find OpenCV, use
    pip show opencv-python
  6. After the training, you may find **"classifier.xml"** in your folder 
  7. Then detection and recognition works smooth
  
